name: ImmaFreedomMod
tagline: For the ImmaFreedom minecraft server located at: play.immafreedom.eu and immafreedom.eu.
body:
# About the server
ImmaFreedom is an associated server of TotalFreedom - The original Free OP Server! We have professional volunteer staff devoted to ensuring a safe, free and friendly community for all ages! Our plugins ensure you're never bored of the same old, same old. We also host custom events, solely dedicated to providing a unique and intriguing experience for all members. Give us a shot, and connect today: play.immafreedom.eu
